# AG Grid version (finosgrid)

- **Target AG Grid version is v35+** — not v33.
- Reference app uses **AG Grid Enterprise** (Set Filter, pivot, **Columns tool panel**, etc.).
- Never use deprecated AG Grid APIs, types, options, or data structures from older majors.
- Before any AG Grid reference app work, docs lookup, or finosgrid parity implementation, use **AG Grid 35+** documentation.

## Parity workflow

For each feature to port into `@widgetstools/finosgrid`:

1. Implement it in an AG Grid **Enterprise v35+** reference app (`apps/ag-grid-reference`).
2. Research AG Grid 35+ docs for API details and use cases.
3. Capture screenshots of the correct look/behavior into `docs/ag-parity/<feature>/`.
4. Only then implement the matching chrome/behavior in finosgrid and compare side-by-side.

## Docs

Prefer current AG Grid React docs for v35+ (column definitions, filtering, floating filters, side bar / columns tool panel, row grouping, theming, etc.) — do not rely on v33-era guidance from global rules when it conflicts with this project rule.
